## IMock.mockHarKey property

Used only when the [mocks format](./kassette.imock.mocksformat.md) is 'har', specifies the key to use inside the har file to either read or write a mock.

**Signature:**

```typescript
readonly mockHarKey?: string;
```

## Remarks

The way the key is stored inside the har file depends on the value of [mocksHarKeyManager](./kassette.imock.mocksharkeymanager.md)<!-- -->.
